<div class="container-fluid image-background" id="why-use-us">
  <div class="image-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="section-header exo white text-center no-margin text-capitalize">Why should I use Euro Bike Tours?</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-container">
  <div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="page-header exo blue text-left no-margin">We've been around the block, so we know a thing or two about organising a cycling trip...</h1>
      <div class="underline"></div>
      <h2 class="sub-header kanit-3 mb3">From the rolling Tuscan hills to the windswept flats of the Netherlands, we pride ourselves on our ability to create just about any imaginable itinerary.</h2>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">Our team has extensive experience of cycling on the continent. If you book a tour with us, you won't find yourself at the roadside with a flat tyre and a soaking wet map written in a foreign language. You will receive a comprehensive pre-tour package, with guidance on everything from local customs, to cycling etiquette, and even the best coffee stops along the way!</p>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">After many years of cycling around Europe, we established a vast network of friends and travel buddies who in turn became our trusted business partners. We have links with local bike shops, cafes, and accommodation, so you will never be too far away from a friendly face.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

